scripts you can run on npm
to run these script use "npm run [script]" inside the terminal while opening the root dir of this project

you need to install all the packages under dependencies and dev-dependencies in package.json first

lint: to run the eslint package on the code to check quality
prettier: to run prettier package on the code and modify it to the specified settings
jasmine: to run the jasmine package for testing
build: to compile the typescript files in the "src" dir and the result will appear in the "dist" directory
test: combining both "build" and "jasmine" scripts
start: to start the server

visit the endpoint images to access the api for the resizing -the server works on port 3500s-

link => localhost:3500/images
